\lim\limits_{n\to\infty}\frac{1}{n}=0
\lim_{n\to \infty}\frac{2}{(1+\frac{1}{n})}=\frac {\lim_{n\to \infty}2}{\lim_{n\to \infty}(1+\frac{1}{n})}= \frac{2}{\lim_{n\to \infty}(1+\frac{1}{n})}=\frac{2}{1}=2
